N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1271.7 - Permission to land or take off jet or turbo-prop aircraft required

State Regulations

No jet or turbo-prop aircraft may land or take off at the
air terminal without permission of Pan American World Airways, Inc. Notes
